cs.DL, cs.IR, cs.CY, cs.SI, cs.LG

The paper discusses the Academic Ranking of World Universities (ARWU), which is based on research performance. Therefore, it is likely to fall under the categories of cs.DL (Digital Libraries), cs.IR (Information Retrieval), and cs.CY (Computers and Society). Additionally, the paper discusses the system of gains and non-linearities used by ARWU, which could also fall under the categories of cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) and cs.LG (Machine Learning).
